{
  "id": "RAW_7c0ee1",
  "title": "用 AI 把一段视频变成可视化网页，Google 的新模型又卷飞了。",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMzA5NjEyMA==&mid=2647670901&idx=1&sn=c7d0f59eb264999fd69b177842ccea27&subscene=0",
  "date": "2025-05-07 01:01:00",
  "author": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "siteName": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Google也不知道受了什么刺激，最近在AI场上，好像越来越有站起来的意思了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">之前我就写过Gemini 2.5 pro，是在</span><a style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMzA5NjEyMA==&amp;mid=2647670278&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=432604996bbe37adc789ce03f87d7e93&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"聊天记录可视化的文章\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" target=\"_blank\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">聊天记录可视化的文章</span></a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">里。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">全世界，只有Gemini 2.5 pro，能吃下一个每天999+微信群聊天记录的上下文，同时还能给你干出，一个还挺好看的可视化网页。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"500187212\" data-ratio=\"0.8520286396181385\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ffeadcc8-2196-42cf-c66f-7590e6610b00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"838\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ffeadcc8-2196-42cf-c66f-7590e6610b00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在Qwen3的跑分中，也印证了，Gemini 2.5 Pro的能力也是真的强。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而我自己在是日常使用中，也几乎是把Gemini 2.5 Pro，变成了我的默认编程模型。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/381e58ce-ce09-4d26-ddf8-91cf5b15d300/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6259946949602122\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1885\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187213\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/381e58ce-ce09-4d26-ddf8-91cf5b15d300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是昨晚，Google好死不死的，又把模型更新了一版，把版本号变成了，Genmini 2.5 Pro（I/O版）。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e31798a0-edff-4637-4ea4-a9d635922600/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.254180602006689\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"598\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187214\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e31798a0-edff-4637-4ea4-a9d635922600/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而在后台的模型调用里，命名是Gemini 2.5 Pro Preview 05-06。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4064021a-e40c-4697-5881-e86f2f021400/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8665850673194615\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"817\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187215\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4064021a-e40c-4697-5881-e86f2f021400/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">现在在Gemini自己的产品官网上，虽然看着还是原来的</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">2.5 Pro (experimental)，但其实背后的模型已经变成</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Gemini 2.5 Pro Preview 05-06了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/dd52696a-76e6-464a-b4e3-0d7648897f00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5204918032786885\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2440\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187217\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/dd52696a-76e6-464a-b4e3-0d7648897f00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">有一说一，Google你的命名到底能不能统一一下。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">真的好乱。。。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而且，Google是真的感觉等不及了，其实距离他们一年一度的I/O大会，也就不到两周时间了，但是还是选择了把新模型直接放出来。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/dc9ad5a4-9064-4bfa-41b3-6891e14ffe00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3952145214521452\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2424\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187216\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/dc9ad5a4-9064-4bfa-41b3-6891e14ffe00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这种行为，一般要么是真牛逼，要么是来吹牛逼。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是Google，这回是前者，是真的有点牛逼。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">他们自己也说了：</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(95, 99, 104);font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;display:inline !important;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;, roboto, arial, helvetica;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: italic;\">We were going to release this update at Google I/O</span></span></span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(95, 99, 104);font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;display:inline !important;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;, roboto, arial, helvetica;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: italic;\">&nbsp;in a couple weeks, but based on the overwhelming enthusiasm for this model, we wanted to get it in your hands sooner so people can start building.</span></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不是我来营销，是真的人民群众需要啊，我只是顺势而为。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这次Gemini 2.5 Pro 05-06版本（后面就简称05-06版了），跟今年三月DeepSeek V3 03-24的更新很像。都是完全为了代码服务的，把代码能力，往上提升了一个巨大的优先级。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而这次的05-06版，我觉得有两个亮点：</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">1. 模型代码能力在盲测竞技场登顶，力压Claude 3.7 Sonnet。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">2. 得益于2.5 Pro强大的多模态能力，这次不仅可以给参考图生成代码，还可以，给参考视频生成代码。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">特别是第二点，目前应该是全球唯一。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">先看看代码能力的跑分。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这次最核心的榜单，就是，WebDev Arena</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">https://web.lmarena.ai/leaderboard</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/06a88fca-8643-469a-991e-c92e3f640800/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8576512455516014\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1405\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187219\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/06a88fca-8643-469a-991e-c92e3f640800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">0506版直接脚踩Claude 3.7 Sonnet，勇得第一。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">可能很多人不知道</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">WebDev Arena是啥，我稍微解释一下，这玩意，还是挺有含金量的。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">LMArena，最著名的大模型盲测竞技场，我相信一直关注AI的，大多数人都或多或少的听过。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">跟一些传统的测试集不一样，这玩意就是纯粹的盲测，用户提出一个Prompt，然后</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">LMArena直接给你两个你也不知道是什么模型生成的回答，让你选你觉得哪个好。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/813978c4-41fc-495f-96e5-79528583ae00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7516985793699815\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1619\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187225\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/813978c4-41fc-495f-96e5-79528583ae00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以，在这上面，你几乎就做不了弊，全靠普通用户，一票一票投出来的，就跟拆盲盒一样。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">WebDev Arena，其实就是一个子榜，还是由</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">LMArena他们开发的，专为评测网页前端开发任务（比如HTML、CSS 和 JavaScript）而设立的。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">玩法跟</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">LMArena一样，也是用户盲测二选一。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">唯一不同的是，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">WebDev Arena会生成代码的预览给你看，而不只是文字了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如我让他生成一个Web的像素猫小游戏。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/973fd6c1-d717-4ebd-6b48-3ce2f2e62300/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.38034398034398037\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2035\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187227\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/973fd6c1-d717-4ebd-6b48-3ce2f2e62300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在等了一分钟两边全部生成完之后，你就能非常明确的看出来，两边哪个是垃圾。。。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9860cace-e3b9-4428-1124-d9ab58d20700/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.622854340362923\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2039\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187228\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9860cace-e3b9-4428-1124-d9ab58d20700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">傻子都能看出来，右边爆杀左边，这个时候，你就为右边，投出神圣的一票就行。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后呢，他们用Bradley-Terry（BT）模型，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">成对对决中的胜负数据，来估算模型的强度，为每个模型计算一个分数，这个分数反映此模型相对于其他模型的获胜概率。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个排名系统非常类似于国际象棋和LOL、王者荣耀里中常用的Elo分。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">只不过在</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">WebDev Arena里，这个分数，叫做Arena Score。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">现在，我们再回过头去看，你就能看到，05-06版，是结结实实提高了147分。。。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4bb1a58c-6e43-4856-5b7e-bc11c085fe00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4309006211180124\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1288\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187229\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4bb1a58c-6e43-4856-5b7e-bc11c085fe00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">研究过王者荣耀或者LOL的影藏分也就是ELO分机制的朋友，就知道，这玩意提升100多分有多难。。。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这一次，Google的Gemini，登顶了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">第二个亮点，也是我觉得很牛逼的，05-06版本，也提升了视频的理解能力，在在VideoMME基准测试中得分为84.8%。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这就带来一个很有趣的化学反应。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">过去我们经常给一个PDF、给一个图片，让它生成一段可视化网页，但是现在，你可以，给一个视频，来变成可视化网页了。。。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不过现在有点BUG，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Gemini官网本身不支持视频的上传，只能在AI Studio里传视频，但而上传的时候，又经常会报错。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4966df04-1731-4d76-c4e3-6406d0711d00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6315331010452961\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1148\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187233\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4966df04-1731-4d76-c4e3-6406d0711d00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Reddit里很多网友也遇到了这个问题。。。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8f134152-f2f9-4470-954a-8743abec1700/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8345558272208639\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1227\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187234\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8f134152-f2f9-4470-954a-8743abec1700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Emmmmm，不过，目前使用YouTube的在线链接生成，目前是可以的。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我们直接打开AI studio的官网：</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">https://aistudio.google.com/</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">模型调整至05-06版。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在加号那，选</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">YouTube。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/737265e9-465b-45a3-d645-0ad6b0f4ba00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.47105788423153694\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1002\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187240\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/737265e9-465b-45a3-d645-0ad6b0f4ba00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我直接扔了一段OpenAI发在</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">YouTube上的Sora教程上去，然后继续用藏师傅的可视化Prompt。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bfca02ac-9306-42b2-9efc-316012c4ca00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6995670995670996\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1155\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187237\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bfca02ac-9306-42b2-9efc-316012c4ca00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">很快啊，代码就跑出来了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我们复制一下，运行看看。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fd71682b-4ae2-4a48-0f4f-7b978a78d400/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6013986013986014\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2002\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187248\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fd71682b-4ae2-4a48-0f4f-7b978a78d400/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">完整版网页在此：https://2uwv6grszo.app.yourware.so/</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">虽然这事，看着很NTR，但是，他真的很酷啊。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这玩意用于学习，你就可以想想，他有多棒。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如我有时候，回去</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">YouTube上看Blender教程。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">现在，我就可以把这个视频和Prompt扔给他。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8957b548-3ec5-43cd-9872-c2e313275100/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7446351931330472\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"932\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500187244\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8957b548-3ec5-43cd-9872-c2e313275100/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">等输出完代码以后，我们看看效果。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"500187250\" data-ratio=\"0.6046296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/41f9434f-092c-4367-b903-426542252b00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/41f9434f-092c-4367-b903-426542252b00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">真的很爽。。。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p data-start=\"70\" data-end=\"120\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以整体来看，这一次Gemini 2.5 Pro 05-06版本，确实是一次非常实在的升级。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"122\" data-end=\"180\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">既有实打实的代码能力提升，也在多模态理解上给到了新可能，尤其是视频转网页这种交叉场景，很可能会带来新的开发范式。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"182\" data-end=\"245\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">当然，Google 现在的问题依然是产品打磨还不够稳，入口混乱、命名迷惑、交互也还有bug，但模型本身的进步，确实值得承认。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"247\" data-end=\"279\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">它已经不是那个只靠PPT和论文刷存在感的Gemini了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"247\" data-end=\"279\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">也不再是每次都被OpenAI狙击的AI界汪峰了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"307\" data-end=\"342\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">接下来就看I/O大会正式发布时。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"307\" data-end=\"342\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Google会不会再放出更大一锤了。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我们，拭目以待。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:var(--articleFontsize);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><strong style=\"white-space-collapse:preserve;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span leaf=\"\">以上，既然看到这里了，如果觉得不错，随手点个赞、在看、转发三连吧，如果想第一时间收到推送，也可以给我个星标⭐～谢谢你看我的文章，我们，下次再见。</span></span></strong></strong></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:left;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"text-wrap:wrap;outline:0px;color:rgb(178, 178, 178);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:12px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-style:solid;text-decoration-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">&gt;/ 作者：卡兹克</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:left;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">&gt;/ 投稿或爆料，请联系邮箱：</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: left;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;att